47:32.973 --> 47:33.714
They couldn't do it.

47:34.338 --> 47:42.170
They would think, well, a God that wants to be personal with me that loves me on a real intimate level, they just couldn't comprehend that in Ephesus.

47:43.172 --> 47:44.894
