47:45.876 --> 47:54.769
So Paul says, now I'm gonna pray for you to have a comprehension that God really loves you, that he's right there with you, that he's close to you, that he wants relationship with you.

47:54.809 --> 47:55.691
This is Paul's prayer.

47:56.833 --> 47:59.497
This is the vision that these people would comprehend these things.

47:59.837 --> 48:02.962
