49:00.217 --> 49:00.978
I had a mom.

49:01.794 --> 49:02.835
And this is what happened.

49:04.537 --> 49:07.882
And then you get born again and you're like, you're still trying to comprehend how much God loves you.

49:07.902 --> 49:08.342
And He does.

49:09.263 --> 49:10.745
