49:10.765 --> 49:14.810
He wants the Ephesian Christians to know this and to grow in this.

49:14.930 --> 49:21.799
It's very important to know the love of Christ that surpasses knowledge He prayed, that surpasses knowledge.

49:22.600 --> 49:24.282
All comprehension is intentional.

49:25.303 --> 49:27.686
Now, watch this because I got a book up here.

49:28.287 --> 49:30.930
It's a book by John MacArthur who went to heaven just recently.

49:31.106 --> 49:32.328
It's called the love of God.

49:32.348 --> 49:33.490
I read this some time ago.

49:35.032 --> 49:36.635
To read this, I had to be intentional.

49:37.436 --> 49:38.237
I had to buy it.

49:38.318 --> 49:41.703
And then when I bought it, then I opened it up and I spent time in it.

49:42.384 --> 49:45.449
And I'm reading it and highlighting it and praying over it.

49:46.090 --> 49:47.733
Comprehension has to be a choice.

49:48.314 --> 49:51.799
You're going to have to say, God, I want to understand your love for me more.

49:52.941 --> 49:53.923
I want you to show me.

49:54.864 --> 49:57.729
The text says the height, the depth, the breadth.

49:57.909 --> 49:58.450
Remember that?

49:59.554 --> 50:04.359
That's not in some manuscripts, that phrase seems to be taken from the Ephesian culture.

50:04.859 --> 50:05.920
Paul, again, is using it.

50:05.960 --> 50:07.642
So it's very wise how he's doing this.

50:08.002 --> 50:10.044
Of course, that's the spirit, giving him that empowerment.

50:12.066 --> 50:15.069
But that would have been understandable to the Ephesian, again, mindset.

50:15.409 --> 50:21.455
So he brings it in and talks about the love of God, the heights and the depths and the breadth of it.

50:22.636 --> 50:23.517
It's a beautiful thing.

50:24.318 --> 50:25.679
So you make a choice.

50:26.200 --> 50:28.562
Who is going to say, you know, all right, God, I need you to show me.

50:28.738 --> 50:30.720
how much you love me, because I really don't feel it.

50:31.441 --> 50:32.743
I really don't understand it deeply.

50:35.987 --> 50:42.375
Committing to the Holy Spirit, cleansing by the Holy Spirit, comprehension of the love of God.

50:43.797 --> 50:48.683
I'm gonna ask you, and somebody can volunteer, put your hand up, if you were willing to read this book.

50:50.024 --> 50:50.385
Anybody?

50:50.866 --> 50:52.287
Okay, right there.

50:53.429 --> 50:54.130
Let me give it to you.

50:54.911 --> 50:57.714
And Lord, I pray in Jesus' name that this book is gonna touch

50:58.530 --> 51:01.935
This dear lady and transform her.

51:04.819 --> 51:06.741
Intentional comprehension is always that.

51:07.022 --> 51:08.223
God, I'm moving towards you.

51:08.704 --> 51:09.325
I want to learn.

51:09.405 --> 51:10.026
I want to grow.

51:10.046 --> 51:11.368
I need you to show me.

51:11.388 --> 51:12.729
I need you to speak to me.

51:12.749 --> 51:15.894
I need you to help me to feel your presence.

51:15.914 --> 51:17.856
All of that is so very important.

51:18.637 --> 51:18.898
Amen.

51:20.540 --> 51:21.081
Conclusion.

51:21.341 --> 51:22.142
Wow, this went long.

51:22.182 --> 51:22.823
I apologize.

51:24.766 --> 51:26.368
I just love talking about these things.

51:26.448 --> 51:27.890
It's so needful, so needful.

51:29.186 --> 51:34.672
There's an impact report I mentioned to you that the vision is just amazing across, that's why we're here, because God led us here.

51:35.033 --> 51:36.715
Thank you for having my wife Lisa and I.

51:37.435 --> 51:39.918
We just love, people ask us all the time, how are things going?

51:39.938 --> 51:40.559
Are you settled in?

51:41.420 --> 51:41.820
What do you like?

51:41.840 --> 51:42.922
What do you love, all that kind of thing?

51:42.962 --> 51:43.823
We just love everything.

51:44.464 --> 51:45.284
And we love all of you.

51:46.466 --> 51:49.830
Even though we don't know most of you and you, I would know your name.

51:50.971 --> 51:53.634
Please help us, we have a meeting right after this for all new people.

51:53.954 --> 51:57.138
Just gonna be down here for 15 minutes called context, step one.

51:57.794 --> 52:00.797
Maybe we'll have a chance to talk more and hang out a little bit more.

52:01.738 --> 52:03.380
You can opportunity pick one of these up.

52:03.400 --> 52:04.101
This is incredible.

52:04.121 --> 52:04.782
This is well done.

52:05.422 --> 52:09.707
This is done by our very own Garrett Rockefeller and others on our team.

52:10.168 --> 52:12.310
And he just talks about what God has done in here.

52:12.330 --> 52:19.578
And there's wonderful picture statistics on how much God has blessed this church, not just upon, but here at this campus and also downtown.

52:19.918 --> 52:21.080
So you'll read through all of this.

52:21.180 --> 52:23.122
At the end, it just shows some more of the financial

52:23.554 --> 52:24.876
Blessings that God has done.

52:24.936 --> 52:30.946
But the heart of our church leadership and the heart of our culture is that we would be filled with the fullness of God.

52:32.167 --> 52:32.568
That's it.

52:33.830 --> 52:35.272
People ask me all the time, what's the vision?

52:35.312 --> 52:35.833
We need vision.

52:35.853 --> 52:37.095
I got so many vision books in there.

52:37.396 --> 52:38.858
You can go in there and look at them if you want.

52:38.898 --> 52:39.619
And I like them.

52:40.480 --> 52:41.562
And I've preached on vision.

52:42.283 --> 52:49.234
But I'm going to tell you, of all the years of ministry, the vision that God has given Dave Ripper and this church,

52:49.730 --> 52:52.334
is by far the most biblical I have ever seen.

52:52.835 --> 52:56.100
Be filled with the fullness of God.

52:57.121 --> 52:59.565
Be filled with the experientially.

52:59.905 --> 53:04.933
That this coming year, this ministry year, we're going to be walking with God in ways that we never thought we could have walked with them.

53:05.994 --> 53:07.236
There's going to be deliverances.

53:07.256 --> 53:08.278
There's going to be healings.

53:08.298 --> 53:09.760
There's going to be reconciliation.

53:10.100 --> 53:12.965
There's going to be things that are going to happen in the supernatural.

53:14.287 --> 53:15.969
But we have to move through these principles.

53:18.513 --> 53:19.154
Submission.

53:20.290 --> 53:23.955
separate yourself from sin and seek the love of God.

53:26.899 --> 53:28.541
And you'll be filled with the fullness of God.

53:29.583 --> 53:30.144
One last thought.

53:31.265 --> 53:35.671
Whatever happened to the church in Ephesus, does anybody know?

53:36.873 --> 53:39.417
Well, you can go to Revelation's chapter two, not now.

53:41.980 --> 53:44.143
Jesus is walking amongst them as the candlestick.

53:44.163 --> 53:46.226
It says the candlestick, that's a reference to Jesus.

53:46.658 --> 53:53.548
And he's walking amongst the churches in Asia Minor, the ones I just quoted a little bit, Pergamum, Smyrna, Laodicea, and he's evaluating all of them.

53:54.569 --> 53:57.233
And he gets to the church in Ephesus and he says some really great things.

53:57.854 --> 54:03.342
You've endured, you've persevered, you did the works of God, but this one thing I have against you.

54:03.362 --> 54:04.163
Do you remember what it is?

54:05.765 --> 54:07.307
They lost their first love.

54:11.173 --> 54:11.733
That's not good.

54:13.736 --> 54:15.058
Father, we pray that you would help us.

54:15.842 --> 54:18.926
We need you desperately, as we sang earlier, depend.

54:19.066 --> 54:20.068
We depend on you.

54:20.128 --> 54:21.349
We can't do this without you.

54:22.210 --> 54:26.316
You want to do far more, far more than we could ever ask or think.

54:26.336 --> 54:27.958
And that's just not about attendance.

54:28.038 --> 54:33.586
That's just not about numbers of money and finances and buildings and all of that.

54:33.606 --> 54:39.954
The far more is an experience with you, a fullness of God that you would fill us.

54:40.098 --> 54:51.555
to capacity as Lloyd Jones, that every faculty that we have, our mind, what we look at, how we talk, our attitudes, our actions, our will, every part of us is consumed by you.

54:53.277 --> 54:54.179
But help us to be honest.

54:55.701 --> 54:58.705
And if we haven't submitted to the Holy Spirit, forgive us, Holy Spirit.

54:59.046 --> 55:00.688
Can we just say that to the Spirit, forgive me.

55:01.590 --> 55:02.671
I'm sorry, Holy Spirit.

55:04.334 --> 55:07.378
Help us to separate from sin, starting today.

55:08.578 --> 55:11.623
and then help us to seek to understand and comprehend the love of God.

55:13.526 --> 55:14.447
Thank you for what you've done.

55:14.467 --> 55:15.629
Thank you for what you're going to do.

55:16.050 --> 55:17.091
So much more is coming.

55:20.016 --> 55:20.637
So much more.

55:20.997 --> 55:21.778
Glory to your name.

55:22.940 --> 55:24.002
And it's in the name of Jesus.

55:24.062 --> 55:24.463
We pray.

55:24.483 --> 55:24.703
Amen.

55:25.484 --> 55:25.705
Amen.

55:25.745 --> 55:26.245
God bless you.

55:30.392 --> 55:34.418
Thanks for listening to the Crossway Christian Church's Middleford campus sermon podcast.

55:34.562 --> 55:41.821
If you like to plug into the life of our community or have any questions that we might be able to answer, visit our website at crosswayscc.org to connect with us.

55:42.282 --> 55:43.545
Until next time, we can be with you.

55:43.846 --> 55:45.490
May the Lord bless you and keep you.

